title: The Landscape Photography Workshop - 2013  UK
description:
The Landscape Photography Workshop - 2013  UK

176 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 10 MB 


The Landscape Photography Workshop aims to take the reader from the very basics of equipment and exposure through to advanced techniques. Landscape essentials, such as composition and filtration, are covered in depth and explained in a precise yet easy-to-understand manner. This book also has chapters dedicated to post-processing and printing, enabling the reader to go successfully from camera to print, plus a number of practical assignments to encourage development.
